Package selection

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RankSelection
    The Class RankSelection performs Rank based selection where we take top two chromosomes bases on the rank of fitness and return it to the GA.
    RankSelectionFactory
    A factory for creating RankSelection objects.
    RouletteWheelSelection
    The Class RouletteWheelSelection performs Roulette wheel selection where we will pick two chromosomes randomly based on the Roulette wheel method and return them to GA.
    RouletteWheelSelectionFactory
    A factory for creating RouletteWheelSelection objects.
    Selection
    The Class Selection which handles selection operation for us.
    SelectionFactory
    A factory for creating Selection objects.
    SteadyStateSelection
    The Class SteadyStateSelection performs Steady state selection where we will pick two random chromosomes from the population.
    SteadyStateSelectionFactory
    A factory for creating SteadyStateSelection objects.
